com.abmash.api.browser

Class Frame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abmash.api.browser.Frame

  • public class Frame
extends java.lang.Object
    Interaction with browser frames, used by calling Browser.frame().

    This class is used to switch the focus between different frames and iframes.

    Author:
    Alper Ortac
